<th>Middle Persian<br /> (<a href="/wiki/Pahlavi_scripts" title="Pahlavi scripts">Pahlavi</a>)<sup id="cite_ref-equal_26-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-equal-26">&#91;i&#93;</a></sup></th>
<th><a href="/wiki/Avestan_alphabet" title="Avestan alphabet">Avestan</a><sup id="cite_ref-equal_26-2" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-equal-26">&#91;i&#93;</a></sup>
